                                                                                                                                 2                                                                                      Pardon ruling
                            
	New Delhi, Sept. 27 (PTI): The Supreme Court has held that a person committing a heinous crime cannot be let off because he or she has been pardoned by the family members of the dead and the panchayat.                                                                                                                                                           
